{"tid":207691,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"抽新股從來未輸過，你問我盡量答","createTime":"2017-04-19T04:41:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T05:39:46.000Z","uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb0d808ebf5ce8ca0b9a8da9e3d89d6422ca4183","tid":207691,"uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T04:41:11.000Z","msg":"印象中07-08年開始抽新股，抽親都賺，獲利率100%，潛水股一係冇落飛，一係在水面走哂。"},{"pid":"ae1cc66265f0faa5447051c736e887118b9e3f88","tid":207691,"uid":29608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T04:42:27.000Z","msg":"點入手必升股？"},{"pid":"c9ff8f8295351945057d9f443a0307cdaf2e4eac","tid":207691,"uid":93245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:17:12.000Z","msg":"新股點揀?"},{"pid":"3ea1719a5df3d4989564e5db6c99705f17a49f44","tid":207691,"uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:14:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點入手必升股？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇下果期興啲乜？<br />\n通常同類型股份，第一隻上的會升<br />\n<br />\n睇下多唔多人抽，（多少即係公眾超額多唔多倍），孖展反應是否熱烈，大銀行是否有做優惠<br />\n<br />\n基石投資者本身的陣容<br />\n<br />\n大股東本身是否狗賊（狗賊唔代表會跌，有時越是賊越升）"},{"pid":"88df615ae6427ca3aef66ea5e715f1fa7f88e20c","tid":207691,"uid":8414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:41:50.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講下戰績?"},{"pid":"52355797cb44e29517a375eba3ab7b0b29ff5119","tid":207691,"uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:36:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可唔可以講下戰績?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實都唔係勁<br />\n<br />\n進階<br />\n松齡<br />\n信達 （好和味）<br />\n弘和 （好驚險）<br />\n美高域<br />\n美圖（得罪講句。on 9才會抽）<br />\n膳源（冇抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n海螺（迫你發達）<br />\n廣發（好和味）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有啲都唔記得了<br />\n<br />\n好和味果啲，未必首日升好多，但分派左好多，升20%都好正"},{"pid":"9897df5920378bf63b55eb7d34893cfd08918fd6","tid":207691,"uid":61770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T16:34:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>